                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable P</hi> 172.) I was at Eltham races, and saw the prisoner attempt several gentlemen's pockets—I watched him, he went behind the prosecutor, took his handkerchief from his pocket, and put it into his right-hand pocket—I took it from him.</p>
               <p>
